data.description: Here is your chance to own a FULLY FURNISHED Destin model, in the popular resort style community of Entrada! Boasting plenty of space, and a huge 3 car garage that the owners have outfitted with an EV charging station, this was the most popular model built in the neighborhood. This home is not only a great floorplan but it has Floratam grass, all new paint inside and out, added gutters, and a brand new roof with an upgraded shingle pattern for better storm protection.This home features a very spacious open concept design with 2,333 sqft. of living space. It features tray ceilings, 4 bedrooms with 3 full bathrooms. The 4th bedroom could also serve as a Den. This home is a Signature Series, so it features many interior upgrades that add the perfect classy touch. Aside from being furnished and ready for occupancy, the sellers also have many extras that are available with the home. These items include a Traeger grill, Blackstone grill, Husqvarna riding lawn mower, and lanai furnishings. A full list of included items will be available at showings. ONE YEAR HOME WARRANTY PROVIDED BY SELLERS. Entrada features very low HOA fees monthly and includes the state of the art amenity center that features a clubhouse with an oversized fitness center, resort style pool with lap lane and splash pad, tennis and pickle ball courts and much, much more.
